{"type": "article", "id": 27669, "title": "模块型收纳柜", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-02T07:27:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702153632zOwtkJIpbho7Augv.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>越来越多的家具开始采用模块型的设计，这款名为 Graphite 的收纳柜正是以此为理念打造而成的。六边形的柜子独立成块，组装起来也并不复杂。成品就像是一个蜂巢，不仅造型时尚，使用起来也非常灵活。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/graphite/graphite-modular-shelves\">众筹链接</a>，3 个模块的早鸟价为 159 欧元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153627bpQmV2WydijkLaJF.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153628r3Zuzp2Pv9moBdHS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153629RvI7oKExSjVFQ68L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153630IAzXjEquU3dQMC0R.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56176471\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}